♫ <i>Romance is fermenting. For you, I’m willing to</i> ♫

463
00:42:20,420 --> 00:42:24,110
♫ <i>Chase away all the troubles</i> ♫

464
00:42:24,110 --> 00:42:27,790
♫ <i>I want to take you to the ends of the earth</i> ♫

465
00:42:27,790 --> 00:42:31,240
♫ <i>I want to listen to your heartbeat</i> ♫

466
00:42:31,240 --> 00:42:34,690
♫ <i>I want to give you a hug</i> ♫

467
00:42:34,690 --> 00:42:38,470
♫ <i>And make the whole world know</i> ♫

468
00:42:38,470 --> 00:42:42,030
♫ <i>Only after meeting you did I realize how important you are to me</i> ♫

469
00:42:42,030 --> 00:42:45,490
♫ <i>No one else can feel your sweetest smile</i> ♫

470
00:42:45,490 --> 00:42:49,260
♫ <i>I don’t need to look for anyone else</i> ♫

471
00:42:49,260 --> 00:42:52,730
♫ <i>Because I’ve already found (you)</i> ♫

