00:42:52,730 --> 00:42:56,400
♫ <i>Our fate just happens to not let anyone else disturb us</i> ♫

473
00:42:56,400 --> 00:42:59,740
♫ <i>Only we know how beautiful our love is</i> ♫

474
00:42:59,740 --> 00:43:03,360
♫ <i>I want to be around you every minute and every second</i> ♫

